    {
      "id": 19226,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "mr_intrusionist discovered an Insecure Direct Object Reference (IDOR) which affects the https://card.starbucks.in/StarbucksMSRModule/starbucksGetCardData.do endpoint through the cardId parameter. This allowed an authenticated, but unauthorized user to iterate cards and view the balance.\n\n@mr_intrusionist — thank you for reporting this vulnerability and confirming the resolution.",
